1447
02:01:25,447 --> 02:01:27,907
They're driving toward you, Gégé.

1448
02:01:28,283 --> 02:01:29,283
Got it.

1449
02:01:29,534 --> 02:01:30,827
Coming up Rue Belliard.

1450
02:01:32,203 --> 02:01:34,622
<i>Coming up Mont-Cenis. We got him.</i>

1451
02:01:36,875 --> 02:01:39,836
In a few days,
I go to Milan with Charlie.

1452
02:01:40,003 --> 02:01:41,004
Milan?

1453
02:01:41,463 --> 02:01:42,464
Why?

1454
02:01:42,672 --> 02:01:45,967
To meet some friends of his.
Red Brigades.

1455
02:01:46,301 --> 02:01:47,343
Not taking me?

1456
02:01:47,719 --> 02:01:49,012
Can't this time.

1457
02:01:50,430 --> 02:01:53,349
The BMW just passed me,
moderate speed.

1458
02:01:53,725 --> 02:01:55,351
<i>Red light at the corner.</i>

1459
02:01:58,688 --> 02:01:59,688
Don't sulk.

1460
02:02:00,231 --> 02:02:02,692
We have a new apartment.
You can fix it up.

1461
02:02:03,067 --> 02:02:04,611
Without you it's no fun.

1462
02:02:11,409 --> 02:02:14,287
The big guy just stopped,
behind three cars.

1463
02:02:14,454 --> 02:02:18,041
Set it up for Clignancourt.
Don't let him on the ring road.

1464
02:02:25,465 --> 02:02:27,008
I won't be gone long.

1465
02:02:32,555 --> 02:02:34,516
<i>Dom here. Coming to Ornano.</i>

1466
02:02:36,434 --> 02:02:37,434
Love me?

1467
02:02:38,186 --> 02:02:39,521
Yes, I love you.

1468
02:02:51,282 --> 02:02:53,076
<i>The light turned green.</i>

1469
02:02:53,243 --> 02:02:54,035
<i>Heads up.</i>

1470
02:02:54,202 --> 02:02:55,537
The BMW is moving.

1471
02:03:01,167 --> 02:03:03,002
<i>Jojo here, headed for Clignancourt.</i>

1472
02:03:06,256 --> 02:03:08,424
<i>I see Clignancourt. We're good.</i>

1473
02:03:34,117 --> 02:03:35,117
Shit!

1474
02:03:36,869 --> 02:03:40,081
Think of that.
I was born not a mile away.

1475
02:03:44,877 --> 02:03:46,796
BMW coming, I see it.

1476
02:03:49,090 --> 02:03:50,216
<i>BMW is on site.</i>

1477
02:03:50,383 --> 02:03:51,634
Goddammit!

1478
02:04:30,256 --> 02:04:31,841
- Go ahead.
- Let him pass.

1479
02:06:16,237 --> 02:06:18,239
Get out!

1480
02:06:18,406 --> 02:06:21,242
I said out!
You don't hear me?

1481
02:06:21,659 --> 02:06:23,453
I said get out.

1482
02:06:23,619 --> 02:06:24,620
My dog!

1483
02:06:26,414 --> 02:06:28,791
On the ground!

1484
02:06:29,625 --> 02:06:31,586
- You killed my dog!
- Don't move!

1485
02:06:34,422 --> 02:06:37,258
You killed my dog,
you assholes!

1486
02:06:38,426 --> 02:06:39,469
Don't move!

1487
02:06:52,356 --> 02:06:53,733
Don't move!

1488
02:06:54,776 --> 02:06:55,776
The cuffs.

1489
02:07:05,119 --> 02:07:06,119
Let's go.

1490
02:07:18,382 --> 02:07:19,550
The dog.

1491
02:07:20,343 --> 02:07:22,094
Get the dog to a vet.

1492
02:07:22,887 --> 02:07:24,722
Seal this all off.

1493
02:07:26,098 --> 02:07:27,892
Where did the truck go?

1494
02:07:34,106 --> 02:07:35,650
It's over.

1495
02:07:35,817 --> 02:07:37,068
He's dead.

